===Background===
[[Image:Visenya takes the Eyrie.jpg|thumb|Visenya Targaryen flew hew dragon directly over the mountains to the Eyrie.]]
Queen Sharra was alongside her son when [[Visenya Targaryen]] flew to [[the Eyrie]] demanding submission, Ronnel bent the knee to [[Aegon I Targaryen|Aegon the Conqueror]] and surrendered the [[Kingdom of the Mountain and the Vale]] in exchange for a ride atop [[Vhagar]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Vale (Histories &amp; Lore)]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
